overview: Myung-soo, who opened a new karaoke room. She promotes the store by giving rice cakes to her local aunts.  In order to take over the strong-looking Myeongsu, the pretty neighborhood ladies start a meat attack. Myung-soo inherits her stamina and leaves the shop to her junior Yoon-il, and Yoon-il is happy at first at the attack of her aunts...
title: Taste of shellfish
